 Java Execution Order – Summary Table
Execution Step  What Runs   When
1️ Static variables (in declaration order) When class is loaded (first time only)
2️ Static blocks   After static variables
3️Instance variables (in declaration order)   Every time object is created
4️ Non-static blocks   After instance variables, before constructor
5️ Constructor After non-static block 



